---
description: graphify before exploration
alwaysApply: true
---

Graph: `graphify-out/graph.json`.

Before Read/Grep/Glob explore:
- `graphify query "<q>"`
- `graphify path "<A>" "<B>"`
- `graphify explain "<concept>"`

Open graph hits only. Skip if editing known lines | missing `graph.json`.

After changes: `graphify update .`. Full rebuild: `/graphify --update`.

Never edit `graphify-out/`.
